{"trainType":"交叉培养","grade":"2020","education":{"id":2,"nameZh":"本科"},"studentType":{"id":4,"nameZh":"普通"},"department":{"id":2,"code":"001","nameZh":"数学科学学院"},"major":{"id":20,"code":"00101","nameZh":"数学与应用数学"},"majorDirection":null,"requiredCredits":16,"awardDegree":true,"beginSemester":"2020年秋季学期","directionGen":true,"moduleTree":[{"self":{"id":30478,"parent":30477,"type":"专业核心课程","typeEn":"Major Courses","major":"--","majorDirection":"--","remark":null,"requiredSubModuleNum":0,"requiredCredits":15,"requiredCourseNum":4,"creditsUpperLimit":null,"courseNumUpperLimit":null,"courses":[{"compulsory":true,"weeks":null,"totalPeriods":60,"theoryPeriods":60,"praticePeriods":null,"experimentPeriods":0,"periodsPerWeek":null,"course":{"id":143513,"code":"MATH3004","nameZh":"泛函分析","nameEn":"Functional Analysis","totalPeriods":60,"theoryPeriods":60,"credits":3,"introduction":"<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 泛函分析是研究具有拓扑结构的无穷维向量空间以及这类空间之间线性映射性质的一门学科, 它是线性代数理论在无穷维情形的自然推广. 目前, 泛函分析已经是学习现代调和分析、多元复分析、偏微分方程、算子代数等学科的数学基础. 这门课主要讲授线性泛函理论, 主要内容涉及: 赋范空间、有界线性算子和有界线性泛函理论、共轭理论、谱理论,特别是紧算子的谱理论.</p>","courseGradation":"专业核心","seasons":"秋"},"terms":[],"remark":null,"examMode":"笔试（闭卷）","department":{"id":2,"code":"001","nameZh":"数学科学学院"}},{"compulsory":true,"weeks":18,"totalPeriods":80,"theoryPeriods":80,"praticePeriods":0,"experimentPeriods":0,"periodsPerWeek":4,"course":{"id":9581,"code":"001013","nameZh":"微分几何","nameEn":"Differential Geometry","totalPeriods":80,"theoryPeriods":80,"credits":4,"introduction":"本课程主要介绍三维欧氏空间中曲线、曲面的经典微分几何，包括第一基本形式、第二基本形式、Gauss曲率和平均曲率、平行移动、测地线、Gauss-Bonnet定理等。","courseGradation":"专业基础","seasons":"秋"},"terms":["0--"],"remark":null,"examMode":"笔试（闭卷）","department":{"id":2,"code":"001","nameZh":"数学科学学院"}},{"compulsory":true,"weeks":18,"totalPeriods":80,"theoryPeriods":80,"praticePeriods":0,"experimentPeriods":0,"periodsPerWeek":4,"course":{"id":9201,"code":"001250","nameZh":"实分析","nameEn":"Real Analysis","totalPeriods":80,"theoryPeriods":80,"credits":4,"introduction":"实分析是关于欧氏空间上的Lebesgue测度和积分理论以及更一般的抽象测度空间上的积分理论的课程，主要内容包括Lebesgue (抽象)测度论和积分论, 收敛定理, Fubini 定理,  Lp空间, Hardy-Littlewood 极大函数, 有界变差函数与绝对连续函数。","courseGradation":"专业基础","seasons":"春"},"terms":["0--"],"remark":null,"examMode":"笔试（闭卷）","department":{"id":2,"code":"001","nameZh":"数学科学学院"}},{"compulsory":true,"weeks":18,"totalPeriods":80,"theoryPeriods":80,"praticePeriods":0,"experimentPeriods":0,"periodsPerWeek":4,"course":{"id":7070,"code":"001010","nameZh":"近世代数","nameEn":"Modern Algebra","totalPeriods":80,"theoryPeriods":80,"credits":4,"introduction":"近世代数又称抽象代数，是高等院校数学系最重要的专业基础课之一，也是线性代数的一门后续课程。近世代数不仅已经成了当代大部分数学的通用语言，在数学中占有极其重要的地位，而且具有丰富的实际应用背景，在相关学科中有着广泛的应用，如理论物理、计算机学科等。其研究的方法和观点，对其他学科产生了越来越大的影响。 近世代数的核心内容是研究方程的解以及由此产生的Galois理论。主要内容为：有限群论，交换环论、域论以及Galois理论。","courseGradation":"专业基础","seasons":"秋,春"},"terms":["0--"],"remark":null,"examMode":"笔试（闭卷）","department":{"id":2,"code":"001","nameZh":"数学科学学院"}}],"public":null,"ref":null,"index":0},"isLeaf":true}]}